{{Chinese|t=大安區|s=大安区|hp=Dà'ān Qū|tp=Dà-an Cyu|w=Ta-an Ch'ü|poj=Tāi-an-khu|altname=Da'anzhuang (old name)|t2=大安莊|s2=大安庄|poj2=Toā-an-chng|
